{"tid":1381555,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"響應「塞爆港島」行動 新巴職工會：正研究進一步行動","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:09:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d48dda0d4b02d921107f690479e9b18c7a2844cf","tid":1381555,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20180906_CR_%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E7%8E%BB%E7%92%83%E7%A2%8E%E8%A3%82_fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20180906_CR_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E7%258E%25BB%25E7%2592%2583%25E7%25A2%258E%25E8%25A3%2582_fb.jpg&h=903dd1f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/20190729_PO_%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2F20190729_PO_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5.jpg&h=952591a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n元朗上周日發生暴力襲擊事件，大批白衣人在元朗站及街頭無差別襲擊市民，警方被批評執法不力，引起眾怒。港鐵超過200名荃灣及觀塘線車長實名簽署，要求警方履行應有之職責，更有傳明日會有罷工行動。新巴職工會表示，將響應《塞爆港島》行動呼籲，正研究進一步行動，請各員工及市民留意事態發展，並呼籲全港巴士從業員明天緊守崗位，安全速度駕駛，緊密照顧傷健、老弱、幼兒及孕婦。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/07/facebook_20190719-CR-%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B41-1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F07%2Ffacebook_20190719-CR-%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25B41-1.png&h=f2319829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n職工會指，就7月21日元朗鐵路站大批市民被毆打，對持械人士襲擊市民表示極度憤怒，對相關執法部門及鐵路公司處理手法表示失望。港鐵經常聲稱自己為世界級鐵路公司，但其對事件的處理手法令人遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n聲明指，過去一星期，政府就元朗事件，多次迴避問題及未有即時作出內部調查，令全港市民感覺恐慌，亦非常憤怒。新巴職工會予以強烈的不滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.bastillepost.com/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2019/03/20190801_cr_%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E5%9F%8E%E5%B7%B4_fb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.bastillepost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fhongkong%2F2019%2F03%2F20190801_cr_%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B7%25B4_fb.jpg&h=2ee0a90b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坪明指，而對於各位不畏強權，以公開姓名參與聯署的港鐵車長，「新巴職工會敬佩你們的智慧及勇氣。港鐵車長們，你們並不孤單，身為巴士從業員的我們也與你們心連心，站於同一陣線。」<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/4807934-%E3%80%90%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E6%9A%B4%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%91%E9%9F%BF%E6%87%89%E3%80%8C%E5%A1%9E%E7%88%86%E6%B8%AF%E5%B3%B6%E3%80%8D%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95-%E6%96%B0%E5%B7%B4%E8%81%B7%E5%B7%A5%E6%9C%83%EF%BC%9A?current_cat=1</code></pre>"},{"pid":"fce6904e0f433f730a20e182a46040763e91e46c","tid":1381555,"uid":11937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:14:21.000Z","msg":"「全港大罷工」動搖唔到經濟民生佔晒全香港都無用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dsovsS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dsovsS</a>"},{"pid":"d70ba84f8e14ebaaec5376a53281ae831fb2a1b3","tid":1381555,"uid":265019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:14:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/23BmZzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F23BmZzz.jpg&h=148695e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwM6rez.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwM6rez.png&h=f8b8de11&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f393ab43053fb0e58cf0d73f72c4878fa80ac97a","tid":1381555,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:56:35.000Z","msg":"多謝新巴工會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13cababb090d0960e833d4c52e63cec42fdc6bb4","tid":1381555,"uid":285774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T10:59:49.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"d8e6ab6e0fecd5650e0c68ed450bdbacb74a5108","tid":1381555,"uid":181789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:02:09.000Z","msg":"九巴呢"},{"pid":"cbeda4f09e2a01952c4bdf8dd3c028a1a8dff72b","tid":1381555,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T11:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}